# Sandbox

```php
<?php
$projectId     = '<project-id>';
$projectSecret = '<project-key>';

// To enable the sandbox
if($sandbox)
    $projectId = 'sandbox-' . $projectId;

$processout = new \ProcessOut\ProcessOut(
    $projectId, $projectSecret);
?>
```

