When developing your application, you might need to troubleshoot
problems which may occur when implementing ProcessOut.

We created a simple-to-use sandbox which lets you send all kinds of
webhooks to your application. To enable the sandbox, all you need to do
is to prepend `sandbox-` to your project id.
The checkout page of invoices you create under the sandbox
will display a list of states that you can trigger. These states,
when triggered, will send a webhook to your application.

<aside class="notice">
When deploying to production, make sure to remove <code>sandbox-</code> and to check that
the webhooks you receive are <strong>NOT</strong> coming from the sandbox.
</aside>
